verses.text:
The blood has been sprinkled, The price has been paid;
The sprinkled blood speaks peace, Forgiveness it hath made;
The sprinkled blood speaks peace, In Jesus' name I stand;
The sprinkled blood speaks peace, For me it cleanses me.

The sprinkled blood gives me boldness, To come to the throne;
The sprinkled blood gives me boldness, To call Jesus my own;
The sprinkled blood gives me boldness, To trust in his word;
The sprinkled blood gives me boldness, To come to my Lord.

The sprinkled blood speaks better things, Than that of Abel's blood;
The sprinkled blood speaks better things, It speaks of Jesus' blood;
The sprinkled blood speaks better things, It speaks of perfect peace;
The sprinkled blood speaks better things, From sin it brings release.
